<p><a name="History" id="History"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Baroque_music&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History</span></h2>
<p><b>Composers of the Baroque</b> <map name="1e85951432e89de2bc508a5b1c7eb174">
<area shape="rect" href="/wiki/Domenico_Alberti" coords="508,778,633,799" title="Domenico Alberti" />
